cstrong data-start=\"382\" data-end=\"408\"\u003e8-Panel Split Wall Set\u003c\/strong\u003e, featuring a legendary blue performance car in a bold, poster-style layout with clean typography, racing stats, and a high-contrast blue\/white\/orange palette.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"756\"\u003eDesigned for \u003cstrong data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"635\"\u003egaming rooms, car setups, studios, and desk walls\u003c\/strong\u003e, the \u003cstrong data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"663\"\u003e4 × 2 split layout\u003c\/strong\u003e creates a premium gallery effect that looks insane from a distance and even better up close.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"781\"\u003eWhat you’ll receive\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"947\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"819\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"819\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"819\"\u003e1 Set = 8 Panels (4 × 2 layout)\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"820\" data-end=\"880\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"822\" data-end=\"880\"\u003eHigh-detail print with sharp textures + racing-poster vibe\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"947\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"883\" data-end=\"947\"\u003ePerfect for desk setups, gaming corners, and garage-themed rooms\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"986\"\u003eSize options (final trimmed size)\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1146\"\u003eWe print on full sheets with small white margins and \u003cstrong data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1065\"\u003emanually trim borders\u003c\/strong\u003e for a clean finish—so the sizes below are the \u003cstrong data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1145\"\u003efinal set size after trimming\u003c\/strong\u003e:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"1147\" data-end=\"1256\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\